==English==

===Noun Phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''stunt double'''

#''Visual entertainment.'' A type of [[body double]], specifically, a skilled stand-in used for dangerous [[film]] or [[video]] sequences, in [[motion picture]]s and [[television]], such as jumping out of a building, jumping from vehicle to vehicle, fight sequences and other sophisticated stunts.

